{"tid":690651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大載中國遊客巴士失事撞石　1死36傷","createTime":"2018-06-05T04:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T07:00:39.000Z","uid":153228,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"633c48a9d458b781a267edb862f4463c3f7f830b","tid":690651,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180605/bknint-20180605070457585-0605_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180605%2Fbknint-20180605070457585-0605_17011_001.html&d=lY5kZ2wbYh2qA7mbLejyKv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=24b147ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180605/bknint-20180605070457585-0605_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180605/photo/bknint-20180605070457585-0605_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180605123048\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180605%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180605070457585-0605_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180605123048&h=61fa2b15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180605/photo/bknint-20180605070457585-0605_17011_001_02b.jpg?20180605123048\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180605%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180605070457585-0605_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20180605123048&h=d500d798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大安大略省一輛載有一批中國遊客的旅遊巴，周一（3日）下午2時30分途經渥太華以南的401公路期間，失事並撞向路邊岩石。一度有指車上37人全部受傷，最新數字指事件造成1人死亡，24人送院，其中5人傷勢嚴重，意外原因仍有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n據報，除了司機外，車上35名遊客及一名領隊均為中國人。旅遊巴車身損毀嚴重，車頭擋風玻璃飛脫，事後停在公路旁一條坑道上。旅遊巴失事撞向路邊岩石時，載有乘客的車身右側位置首當其衝，故損毀嚴重，亦令大部分遊客受傷。警方指，涉事的司機上班僅一個月，事件並不涉及其他車輛。<br />\n<br />\n事發後部分傷者血流披面待救。有目擊者形容，「這輩子從未見過如此恐怖的意外」。中國駐加拿大使館發言人楊雲東表示，中國駐加使館對意外高度重視，並已啟動應急機制，與加拿大有關部門聯繫並核實有關情況。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，受傷的旅客正參加一個10天旅行團，由華盛頓出發，事發時經401公路，前往多倫多。事發後，當地政府出動多輛救護車及三架醫療直升機到場運送傷者，並將情況較嚴重的傷者送往布羅克維爾、京士頓、肯普特維爾及渥太華的醫院，而受輕傷的旅客則被送往渥太華的皇后道卡林頓醫院。"},{"pid":"a0e3a962c45e12fc3b4b6d4a38ca9f6a0f7df9ab","tid":690651,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4876578425a6f77d3260997db0b3496205238b08","tid":690651,"uid":125237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:16:06.000Z","msg":"點解唔係37死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9fd3e1fb5f0d6f40da3d1e07d62274c4cc56e0","tid":690651,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:16:38.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"8d43930ead67434d8cded4adf46efb9699587a52","tid":690651,"uid":121409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:17:21.000Z","msg":"司機有冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad951b84b40282023420f16c9f75383b0fc79fce","tid":690651,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d43930ead67434d8cded4adf46efb9699587a52","tid":690651,"uid":121409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:17:21.000Z","msg":"司機有冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"好理解佢想整死班蝗蟲，可惜佢低估左班螂既生命力"},{"pid":"de71f6ecc0821052f06ece85c5b05b3af32ba3e1","tid":690651,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"司機應該硬唔順班支那大媽 係咁傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdfbc8f8ba93c30339ad46d226fd6dc8456c5be","tid":690651,"uid":66501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de71f6ecc0821052f06ece85c5b05b3af32ba3e1","tid":690651,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"司機應該硬唔順班支那大媽 係咁傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T07:00:39.000Z","msg":"完全feel到個司機比班蝗嘈到渣唔到車"}]}